{
  "version": "2025-10-31T11:20:00-05:00",
  "description": "CENTRAL: season+zone garden layouts, care & harvest profiles for Suka Smart Assistant. Auto-fed by scrapers/ingestors, with hub override for Torah/culture-specific rules. Feeds Garden Planner, GardenQueueManager, Storehouse/Inventory intake, Meal Planner (from harvest), Cleaning (tool+area sanitation), and Animal (grazing/pest) integrations.",
  "meta": {
    "sourceOfTruth": "scraper",
